oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Green Grocery Company delivery truck
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of two unidentified men with a Green Grocery Company delivery truck that is parked on a street. One man sits in the driver's seat, and another is unloading groceries. Text on the side of the truck says: "Quality service / We are busy / Green Grocery Co.," as well as "Bell 178-27 / Citz. 192-40." Homes are visible along the street in the background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Men; Automobiles; Houses; Delivering; Utility poles
